org.sbml.squeezer.kinetics

Interface InterfaceIntegerStoichiometry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InterfaceKinteticsType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HillEquation, IrrevNonModulatedNonInteractingEnzymes

    public interface InterfaceIntegerStoichiometry
extends InterfaceKinteticsType
    All implementing classes represent kinetic equations that require all participating species to take part with integer stoichiometry (reactants and products). (2009-09-24)
    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger
